4. **Documentation Triggers**
```typescript
   interface DocumentationTriggers {
     code_changes: {
       inline_docs: 'auto-update';
       readme: 'sync-changes';
       api_docs: 'regenerate';
     };
     feature_updates: {
       documentation: 'auto-refresh';
       examples: 'regenerate';
       diagrams: 'redraw';
     };
     dependency_changes: {
       requirements: 'auto-update';
       compatibility: 'verify';
       security: 'assess';
  };
}
```

5. **Documentation Locations**
   - Root Level
     ```
     /
     ├── README.md (Project overview)
     ├── ARCHITECTURE.md (System design)
     └── CHANGELOG.md (Auto-updated changes)
     ```
   - Feature Level
     ```
     /src/app/
     ├── api/
     │   ├── README.md (API documentation)
     │   ├── ROUTES.md (Route documentation)
     │   └── SECURITY.md (API security)
     ├── components/
     │   ├── README.md (Component library)
     │   └── USAGE.md (Component examples)
     └── features/
         ├── auth/
         │   ├── README.md (Auth documentation)
         │   └── FLOW.md (Auth flow diagrams)
         └── dashboard/
             ├── README.md (Dashboard docs)
             └── METRICS.md (Performance data)
     ```

